<p>英 /'tʃɪəfl/    美 /'tʃɪrfl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>兴高采烈的；高兴的；令人愉快的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She told me to be cheerful and look on the bright side.
她劝我高兴点儿，要看到乐观的一面。</p><footer>译林⑤ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a bright, cheerful restaurant
明亮宜人的餐馆</p></div>

